These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk
Pet: pony, frog, lizard, fish
1. Pet:fish is on the left of Beverage:cola##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Pet:frog##1
3. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:lizard is on the left or right of Pet:fish##3
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | almond-milk | cola |
| Pet        | pony | frog   | fish | lizard    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: time-travel, spy, horror, zombie
Nationality: italian, egyptian, thai, american
1. Movie-Genre:spy is on the left of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
2. Nationality:italian is on the left of Nationality:thai##1
3. Nationality:thai is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:italian == Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
5. Nationality:egyptian is on the right of Nationality:thai##1
6. Nationality:italian == Movie-Genre:time-travel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | time-travel  | spy  | zombie |
| Nationality   | american    | italian | thai | egyptian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: broccoli, nectarine, asparagus, zucchini
Movie-Genre: comedy, drama, time-travel, family
1. Food:zucchini is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family##3
2. Food:asparagus is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:family is on the left or right of Food:nectarine##3
4. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
5. Movie-Genre:comedy is in an odd position##4
6. Food:nectarine is on the right of Food:asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | zucchini | asparagus | nectarine    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel        | family     | comedy | drama |

