.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: card-games, baking, chess, gardening
Music-Genre: salsa, r&b, funk, electronic
1. Hobby:baking is between Music-Genre:salsa and Music-Genre:electronic##2
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
3. Music-Genre:funk is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left of Music-Genre:electronic##1
5. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening | card-games | baking | chess |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | salsa   | r&b    | electronic  |

