2. Nationality:indonesian == Music-Genre:r&b##1
3. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Music-Genre:reggae##1
4. Music-Genre:indie is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:metal is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | reggae    | metal   | r&b       |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | argentine | indonesian |

