3. Movie-Genre:crime is on the left of Movie-Genre:horror##1
4. Transport:scooter == Movie-Genre:documentary##1
5. Movie-Genre:crime is on the left or right of Transport:tram##3
6. Transport:trike is on the right of Transport:tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime | horror | superhero    |
| Transport     | scooter | train  | tram     | trike |

