2. Job:manager is in an odd position##4
3. Pet:dog is on the left or right of Job:manager##3
4. Job:manager is on the right of Pet:dog##1
5. Job:electrician is between Job:manager and Job:accountant##2
6. Pet:chinchilla is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:chinchilla is between Job:electrician and Pet:rat##2
8. Job:electrician is on the left or right of Job:accountant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | accountant | electrician      | manager | chef |
| Pet   | goldfish  | dog | chinchilla    | rat            |

