.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: lemonade, sprite, tea, hot-chocolate
Music-Genre: metal, soul, punk, hip-hop
1. Beverage:lemonade == Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
2. Music-Genre:metal is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
3. Music-Genre:hip-hop is between Music-Genre:metal and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:lemonade is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left or right of Music-Genre:metal##3
6. Beverage:sprite is on the left or right of Music-Genre:soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite       | tea   | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | punk | soul | hip-hop        | metal    |

