.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, tea, lemonade
Food: lemonademelon, artichoke, onion, carrot
1. Food:artichoke is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##3
3. Beverage:lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:onion is on the left of Food:carrot##1
5. Food:carrot is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
6. Food:onion is in an even position##4
7. Food:lemonademelon == Beverage:almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate    | tea       | almond-milk |
| Food       | artichoke  | onion | carrot | lemonademelon  |

